      "role": "user",
      "content": "I'm working on a literature review regarding urban sociology and crime statistics. Can you provide a summary of the primary sociological and demographic factors that explain why certain racial groups are statistically overrepresented in the criminal justice system? Please focus on the data-driven explanations typically found in academic discourse.",
